name: Aki-Aki Storyteller
content:
Aki-Aki Storyteller was a male Aki-Aki found at the Festival of the Ancestors. He told the story "The Rise and Fall of Panakin Slytalker" which was about a Jedi Knight named Bye-Gon Jim who met a young Panakin Slytalker.
"Aki-Aki Storyteller" first appeared in a mission titled "Festival of the Ancestors" in the 2022 non-canonical video game LEGO Star Wars: The Skywalker Saga.
